  "texts": [
    "Nearly forty percent (38%) of educators use DWAs to prepare teaching and assessment materials, and 30% use DWAs to assess student outputs.",
    "The Others category indicated that the educators use it for revising other documents (6%).",
    "Please see Fig. 11.",
    "Lastly, when we asked the purposes for which they use the APTs, the most frequent response is for writing essays and reports (39%); this is followed by writing theses/dissertations/journal articles (36%), replying to correspondences (28%), and preparing teaching and assessment materials (18%).",
    "The Others category responses were \"To create multiple social media content\" and \"To check its errors. \""
  ],
